These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, punk, electronic, dubstep
1. the fan of punk is between the fan of electronic and the fan of dubstep##2
2. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
3. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | funk | dubstep | punk | electronic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, coffee, soy-milk, lemonade
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | coffee | lemonade | tea | soy-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: horse, mouse, goldfish, lizard
1. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the lizard##2
3. the owner of the horse is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | horse | lizard | goldfish | mouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
