1. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking water and the person drinking juice##2
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | water | milk | juice | sprite |

 